The Concept arrays, Data types The concept arrays are a little bit different
The delegates, Data types Delegates are functions contained by an object (by object you should understand an instantiated class) that are referenced by a variable
The static number type, Data types Static numbers are represented internally on 64 to 80 bits(8-10 bytes) depending on the version and operating system used
The static string type, Data types Concept strings are autoallocable (you don't need to allocate them)
